<span class="regex-highlight comment">% create_ring will return the data structure which is used</span>
<span class="regex-highlight comment">% for all of the ring functions. This is essentially a list of</span>
<span class="regex-highlight comment">% Pid's for processes which have already been spawned and are</span>
<span class="regex-highlight comment">% waiting for a message from the previous process in the ring.</span>